# Subscription Management Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   get_subscriptions — Get all active subscriptions for the Apple ID
#   modify_subscription — Upgrade, downgrade, or cancel a subscription
#   get_plan_options — Get available plan options for an Apple service
#   check_billing_history — View billing history for subscriptions
#   resolve_billing_issue — Investigate and resolve a billing dispute
